headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From AbbVie’s Q3 Earnings Call
summary: AbbVie’s third quarter results were marked by strong year-on-year revenue growth, driven primarily by continued momentum in its immunology and neuroscience portfolios. Management pointed to sales growth from Skyrizi and Rinvoq, as well as double-digit expansion in neuroscience products, as key contributors to the performance.
